{"word":"ψόγος","slug":"ψόγος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ψόγος</b></el> <el>(ψόγος, ὁ,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><el>ψέγω</el>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>a blamable fault, a blemish, flaw</i>, <b><a href='S:Simonides Lyricus'>Simon.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>blame, censure</i>, <b><a href='S:Pindar'>Pind.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Tragic, in Tragic Greek'>Trag.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>; <el>ψόγον τινὶ ἐπενεγκεῖν</el> <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}